examples.en: His latest book reveals hidden talents.
His mature work reveals a deep sense of enjoyment of nature.

The author inadvertently reveals the murderer in the penultimate chapter.

The book reveals the cold calculations that were behind the government's policies.
The method also reveals any cannibalism between shops or branches of the same company.
